  "intent_precise": "qPCR GCN Prep: Using Tube Rack (tuberack, slot 4), DNA Plate (pcr_plate, slot 2), qPCR Plate (pcr_plate, slot 1). (1) Mix 1 times at 22\u00b5L in Tube Rack A1. (2) Transfer 22\u00b5L from Tube Rack A1 to qPCR Plate A1. (3) Mix 1 times at 22\u00b5L in Tube Rack B1. (4) Transfer 22\u00b5L from Tube Rack B1 to qPCR Plate A1. (5) Mix 1 times at 22\u00b5L in Tube Rack C1. (6) Transfer 22\u00b5L from Tube Rack C1 to qPCR Plate A1. (7) Mix 1 times at 3\u00b5L in Tube Rack D5. (8) Transfer 3\u00b5L from Tube Rack D5 to qPCR Plate A1. (9) Mix 1 times at 3\u00b5L in Tube Rack A6. (10) Transfer 3\u00b5L from Tube Rack A6 to qPCR Plate A1. (11) Mix 2 times at 10\u00b5L in qPCR Plate A1. (12) Mix 1 times at 3\u00b5L in Tube Rack B6. (13) Transfer 3\u00b5L from Tube Rack B6 to qPCR Plate A1. (14) Mix 2 times at 10\u00b5L in qPCR Plate A1. (15) Mix 1 times at 3\u00b5L in Tube Rack C6. (16) Transfer 3\u00b5L from Tube Rack C6 to qPCR Plate A1. (17) Mix 2 times at 10\u00b5L in qPCR Plate A1. (18) Mix 1 times at 3\u00b5L in Tube Rack D1. (19) Transfer 3\u00b5L from Tube Rack D1 to qPCR Plate A1. (20) Mix 2 times at 10\u00b5L in qPCR Plate A1. (21) Mix 1 times at 3\u00b5L. (22) Transfer 4\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (23) Mix 2 times at 10\u00b5L.",
  "intent_concise": "Perform 9 liquid transfers. (volumes 3\u00b5L-22\u00b5L)",
  "intent": "For the qPCR GCN Prep, you'll be working with the tube rack in slot 4, DNA plate in slot 2, and qPCR plate in slot 1. Start by mixing and transferring 22\u00b5L each from tube rack positions A1, B1, and C1 into qPCR plate well A1, then add 3\u00b5L each from tube rack positions D5 and A6, mixing twice at 10\u00b5L in the qPCR plate after the A6 addition. Continue adding 3\u00b5L from tube rack positions B6, C6, and D1 in sequence, mixing twice at 10\u00b5L in the qPCR plate after each addition. Finally, perform one more mix at 3\u00b5L, transfer 4\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1, and finish with two final mixes at 10\u00b5L.",
